      "rationale": "Code verification performed via patch tests for linear elasticity, standard Timoshenko beam benchmark, and contact patch test. All three FEA implementations (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) produced results within 0.1% of analytical solutions for the verification benchmarks. Order-of-convergence tests confirmed expected quadratic convergence for hexahedral elements used in the screw shank.",
      "acceptanceCriteria": {
