      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "rationale": "Nonlinear solver convergence monitored via force and displacement residual norms (tolerance 1×10⁻⁴). All load steps converged within 15 iterations. Energy norm residual < 1×10⁻⁶ at final converged state. Direct sparse solver (PARDISO) used for linear system; iterative refinement applied. No divergence or non-convergence events observed across all 11 model instances.",
      "acceptanceCriteria": {
        "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/ac/numerical-solver-error",
        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "description": "Force and displacement residual norms must be < 1×10⁻³ at convergence. Energy norm residual must be < 1×10⁻⁵. All load steps must converge without manual intervention. Gradation 2 requires documented convergence monitoring with residual history."
      }
