      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "rationale": "Model setup independently reviewed by a second analyst at each of the three participating organizations. Boundary conditions, material assignments, contact definitions, and load application verified against the ASTM F1717 standard and internal modeling protocol SOP-FEA-003. Discrepancies found in initial contact stiffness specification were resolved prior to final analysis runs. Signed review checklists archived in project document management system.",
      "acceptanceCriteria": {
