      "rationale": "Material properties (E, ν, σ_y, E_t) measured from coupon specimens machined from the same material lots as the test constructs. Geometric dimensions measured from CMM scans of three representative screws and rods (mean ± SD reported). UHMWPE block compressive modulus measured per ASTM D695 (n=5). All input values traceable to calibrated measurement equipment with current calibration certificates. Uncertainty in material inputs quantified and propagated in UQ analysis.",
      "acceptanceCriteria": {
        "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/ac/model-inputs",
        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "description": "Material properties must be measured from same material lots as test specimens. Geometric inputs must be from dimensional inspection of representative hardware. All inputs must be traceable to calibrated measurement systems. Gradation 2 requires documented input traceability."
