      "rationale": "N=11 non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs tested, drawn from the same production lot as the device intended for regulatory submission. Constructs assembled per manufacturer IFU by trained lab personnel. Sample size provides statistical power > 0.80 to detect a 10% difference in mean stiffness at α=0.05 (power analysis documented in Test Plan TP-2024-NC-001). Both laboratories used identical hardware from the same lot.",
      "acceptanceCriteria": {
        "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/ac/test-samples",
