        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "description": "Model inputs must be demonstrably equivalent to experimental conditions. Fixture geometry, assembly torques, and boundary conditions must be verified against test documentation. Gradation 2 requires documented cross-check between test and model input parameters."
