      "rationale": "Quantitative comparison performed for all three QoIs (stiffness, yield force, force at 40 mm) using both percentage difference (< 10% threshold) and E/uval metric (< 1.96 threshold). All QoIs meet both acceptance criteria. Comparison documented in Validation Report VR-2024-NC-001 with tabulated results, force-displacement curve overlays, and statistical summary. Inter-laboratory reproducibility assessed; CV < 6% for all QoIs across both laboratories.",
